“What GD?” filters browser’s history to show links on Google Docs™, Google Sheets™, Google Forms™, Google Slides™, and diagrams.net opened by a user in Google Chrome.

The most recent history (up to 10 days) is displayed in a popup when a user clicks the extension icon.
The “See more results” link at the bottom of the popup opens a new tab with Google Docs™, Google Sheets™, Google Forms™, Google Slides™, and diagrams.net opened within the last 90 days.

Google Docs™, Google Sheets™, Google Forms™, and Google Slides™ are trademarks of Google LLC.
